release_note: This version includes an enhancement to the recording and bug fixes. Remember you can record your encrypted voice notes for as long as you want and track your journaling activity in the new dashboard. You can also turn on the mood analyzer which shows you a mood breakdown and scale solely based on your audio input! As always please do not hesitate in reaching out to our friendly team at contact journify.co.

TRY THE FIRST AUDIO MOOD ANALYZER! With this new version of Journify you ll be able to track your journaling activity in the dashboard and turn on the mood analyzer. This is a feature that helps you track your mood over time based on your audio content without any additional input required . This version also has a smoother experience for subscriptions online transcripts and we finally removed the warnings at 30 minutes! You can now freely record as long as you want without interruptions. As always please do not hesitate in reaching out to our friendly team at contact journify.co.

This version of Journify includes a better experience for anyone recording over 30 minutes. Sometimes our minds have a lot to say! Remember that those long recordings can also be transcribed live if you re online and then exported or shared with any other apps on your phone Notion Google Drive Whatsapp Email etc .

This update includes performance improvements to your audio journaling offline experience great for when your connection is failing you or when you decide to audio journal on the train . When you re offline you can still record and save your entries in the same way. You can also request a transcript as soon as you re back online.

This version of the app includes performance updates to our recorder while maintaining the option to get live transcripts of your entries. It also allows you to listen to music or other form of audio and then continue recording your journal entries. As always if you have any questions please email us at contact journify.co.

BEST AUDIO TO TEXT TRANSCRIPTS Hey Audio Journal Fans!! Thank you for choosing Journify to track your life s journey. We are working hard to make audio journaling with Journify effortless and offer you the best experience possible so we have some exciting new features to share with you. We hope you love them! And even if you don t we still want to hear from you. We re prioritizing our product roadmap based on YOUR feedback. On this new version you will be able to transcribe any of your audio journal entries. No need to say comma or period when you re recording. Our app is smart enough to get that in for you! Once your transcripts are ready you can also share them via email text WhatsApp or save them to your Google Drive.
